dct_title_s: Pictorial map of Copnehagen old town
dct_description_sm: Map shows sites of tourist attractions, streets are named. Only selected buildings and features are shown pictorialy. Tourist Association of Copenhagen. Only selected buildings and features are illustrated. Index for points of interest on lower margin. Verso: second map of Copenhagen. Note: Bird's eye is in English, verso is in Danish with some English explanation.
dct_publisher_sm: [Copenhagen] : Dansk arbejdes københavns-udvalg og politikens forlag, [1955].
